media:group.media:description:
Pizza Wars is back with a bang! On the Season 4 premiere, Nicole Russell must create a pizza spicy enough to make Hot Ones host Sean Evans break a sweat. Will Nicole’s Nashville hot chicken-inspired slice bring home the golden pizza trophy, or will she lose out to Down North Pizza's Mike Carter and his Thai curry-smothered Detroit pie? Only Sean can decide!
